This package bundles tokenizer assets derived from official Hugging Face repositories under the cerebras organization:
- cerebras/Cerebras-GPT-111M tokenizer.json
- cerebras/btlm-3b-8k-chat tokenizer.json

The model aliases cerebras/Cerebras-GPT-256M, cerebras/Cerebras-GPT-590M, cerebras/Cerebras-GPT-1.3B, cerebras/Cerebras-GPT-2.7B, cerebras/Cerebras-GPT-6.7B, cerebras/Cerebras-GPT-13B, and cerebras/btlm-3b-8k-base are mapped to bundled tokenizer snapshots after hash verification.

